# Frontend Conventions

## Directory

Primary: `frontend/` — the ONLY active frontend directory.

```
frontend/src/
  components/   # Reusable UI components (@/components/ui)
  features/     # Feature modules (auth, call, chatbot, dashboard, inbox, knowledge, quality, summary, admin)
  hooks/        # Custom React hooks
  stores/       # Zustand state management
  config/       # Configuration
  i18n/         # Internationalization (en, ko, ja, zh-CN)
  lib/          # Utilities (api.ts for Axios client)
frontend/e2e/   # Playwright E2E tests
```

## Deprecated — NEVER Reference

- `apps/web/` — legacy, ignore entirely
- `packages/` — legacy, ignore entirely

## Tech Stack

- React 18, TypeScript, Vite 6
- Tailwind CSS, custom components in `@/components/ui`
- Zustand (stores), TanStack Query (data fetching), react-i18next
- Routes defined in `src/App.tsx` (React Router)

## Dev Commands

```bash
cd frontend && pnpm install && pnpm dev   # http://localhost:4501
pnpm build
pnpm test:e2e
```

Backend APIs are proxied through Vite config. Auth handled by `services/admin/`.
